edited by A. Bowie, Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</li>

<li>Schopenhauer, A., 1995. <em>On the Basis of Morality</em>,
Providence: Berghahn Books.</li>

<li>Simmons, A., 2014, &ldquo;In Defense of the Moral Significance of
