271&ndash;314.</li>

<li>Stueber, K., 2006, <em>Rediscovering Empathy: Agency, Folk
Psychology, and the Human Sciences</em>, Cambridge, MA: MIT
Press.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2008, &ldquo;Reasons, Generalizations,
Empathy, and Narratives: The Epistemic Structure of Action
