<em>Psychological Bulletin</em>, 52: 1&ndash;23.</li>

<li>Titchener, E. B., 1909, <em>Lectures on the Experimental
Psychology of Thought-Processes</em>, New York: Macmillan.</li>

<li>Tully, J. (ed.), 1988. <em>Meaning and Context: Quentin Skinner
